metadata.shortInfo: Clustered cDNAs from this species provided by Nematode.net that have been aligned to the genome using STAR.  Nematode.net (http://nematode.net/) is a part of the parasitic nematode EST project at The Genome Institute at Washington University in St. Louis. The site was established in 2000 as a component of the NIH-NIAID grant 'A Genomic Approach to Parasites from the Phylum Nematoda'.
